SDLC = Software Development Life Cycle  => is a process that follow ,
process  Planing => Defining => Desining => Building => Testing => Deployment 
Most import process in DEOPS is 1] Building
                                2] Tesing
                                3] Deployment

Know this 3 proces is Automation by using Deops not manually
They are th pillor of the DeOps 

**** Interview Q

1] What is the pillor of devOps ?
DevOps engineer is primarily focused on Automations of Building, testing and Deployment by writing automation Scripts thereby avoiding manual intervention, 
so that it will improve efficiency and reduces the time for application delivery......
